{
  "stem": "198.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was on the border of Germany and Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got there by train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrived to that camp, it was-- [SIGHS] They told us, you don't have to worry about your life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we knew that we don't have to worry about our life, that we won't live too long.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got to the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were two hundred girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they set us up in barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We all were young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had German SS watching over us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was in Czechoslovakia, in Bad Kudowa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Always held on to my sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was with me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Was lucky.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they sent us up in the barracks, and then they sent us to work to ammunition plant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a plant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It looked like mountains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were 200 girls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the plant they were working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were producing the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was quite intelligent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I knew the German language very well, because I went to a very good school in Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So sort of they picked me I should be an interpreter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they gave me a little bit of extra bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was an interpreter for a few months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, I recall one incident that the German said, I just can't understand what they did [SOBBING] with you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're so intelligent.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did they do to you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Remember when we came to the factory at concentration camp, they had big signs on the walls.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said don't speak with those girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They whores.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came from a prison.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why they came to concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But some--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
